rldview.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jul 2022) 0aEconomic policy. 0aEconomics. 0aLiberalism. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / General.2bisacsh1 aLewis, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLewis, Paul, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311073919040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226781471423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226781471/original  a978-3-11-073919-0  University of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles